race.comment: CURLY DANGER (6) turned in a moderate effort last time when fifth at this track over 278m behind Secrets Revealed (16.49) in a Grade 4. Can atone. BONTA (1) turned in a fair run last time from the squeeze finishing fifth by 3.5 lengths (20.26). Great chance to atone. BUCKLE UP GAVIN (2) has been out of the placings last couple but impressed when clocking a 29.86 over 515m at this track three starts back. Expecting another bold showing. KAMLOOPS (7) can improve on an unplaced run here last time out.
